#week-title("Four", "The Divine Triangle & Life-Path Mapping")

=== Core Teaching

The final week of this month introduces the *Divine Triangle* as an alchemical
framework for mapping personal cycles. Just as we map the laboratory work onto
the Tree of Life, we use numerology to map the stages of our own development.

By understanding your life-path structure, you can identify years of crisis,
breakthrough, and harvest — allowing you to time your Great Work with greater
precision.

=== Topics This Week

- The Divine Triangle: Drawing and labelling the blueprint
- Life-path mapping as an alchemical cycle
- Review of the second quarter's progress

#inner-work[
  *Mapping the Blueprint*

  Draw your own Divine Triangle using the instructions in Javane & Bunker's
  text. Identify your current "Personal Year" within the context of your overall
  life blueprint.

  How does your current life cycle align with your alchemical work? Record your
  mapping and interpretation in your journal.
]

